2 The decision of the executive board to install an electric vehicle charging station
3 is [an agenda item listed for discussion;] ratified by units’ owners in accordance
4 with the provisions of subsection 2;
5 (3) The association complies with the provisions of subsection 3 of NRS
6 116.345; and
7 (4) Placement of the electric vehicle charging station in that location
8 does not [increase any cost to any unit owner or] violate any applicable zoning
